{"tid":561432,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"［短故］情人節那天，我吃了一碟粟米肉粒飯","createTime":"2018-02-15T04:12:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-02T01:44:44.000Z","uid":42927,"like":24,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"1956ea4fc7f613f5b9727cf8d532d0bf8854d3a7","tid":561432,"uid":42927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T04:12:01.000Z","msg":"某夜，甫下班的我走到一間茶記，打算吃一碟粟米肉粒飯。<br />\n<br />\n「靚仔，幾多位呀？」在門口迎接我的是一位操着純正廣東話的姨姨。<br />\n<br />\n「一位。」我伸出一隻手指，微微笑著。<br />\n<br />\n「是但坐啦。」她一邊說道，然後一邊自顧自的看著掛在店內角落正發光的電視機。<br />\n<br />\n我挑了卡位，施施然的坐下，只見店內僅有寥寥數人，一位貌似是廚師的人正坐在廚房的門口抽著煙，茶記之內應有的聲音霎時頓失，這氣氛顯得有點冷清。<br />\n<br />\n「唔該～」我示意著要姨姨過來。<br />\n<br />\n「食咩？」她問，但雙眸的目光仍離不開那部電視機。<br />\n<br />\n「一碟粟米肉粒飯，飲凍檸茶少甜。」我說。<br />\n<br />\n她聽罷，便掏出紙筆，快快的寫下來。<br />\n<br />\n又唸唸有詞的重複地說著我點的餐。<br />\n<br />\n忽爾，她像是搭訕的問：「今日冇拖拍咩？」<br />\n<br />\n我心裡一奇，反問道：「拍咩拖呀？」<br />\n<br />\n「今日情人節呀嘛。」<br />\n<br />\n「嗯⋯⋯乜係咩？」<br />\n<br />\n我不禁失笑，心中更起了個疑問；難道情人節就一定要拍拖的嗎？<br />\n<br />\n「咁你呢阿姨？唔洗陪老公咩？」我淡淡的問。<br />\n<br />\n「唔洗做咩？哈哈哈⋯⋯」她說罷便大笑起來，這一笑，很擾人。<br />\n<br />\n雖爾，她說得對，人要返工亦屬正常之事，為了吃飯糊口，也得返工。<br />\n<br />\n但久而久之，生活就剩下「某夜」。<br />\n<br />\n連「這天」也說不出、分不清、活不好。<br />\n<br />\n人大了，對於節日或重要日子亦不再敏感，可能是性格使然，又或是不自覺地被刻板勞累的生活所淹沒了。"},{"pid":"ee1895d56533e828460ca2e2ebd70db0a812f5a6","tid":561432,"uid":42927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T04:12:26.000Z","msg":"真係短故嚟"},{"pid":"f7540436b699d7d37330d74ebbbd0bf74f9e2690","tid":561432,"uid":42927,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T04:50:27.000Z","msg":"頃刻，一碟冒著熱氣的粟米肉粒飯和一杯少甜凍檸茶已放到我的眼前。<br />\n<br />\n我拿起鐵羹，舀起一勺淡黃色的粟米汁倒在白飯上，稍稍混和一下，接著便舀起一口沾滿汁液的的肉粒和飯粒放進口裡細嚼。<br />\n<br />\n老實說，我真的很愛吃這碟頭飯。<br />\n<br />\n很愛很愛⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n不僅是愛著味道，還愛著一份回憶。<br />\n<br />\n甜甜的粟米汁，以蛋花與粟米粒製成，入口時能與飯粒融為一體。<br />\n<br />\n而味道亦不濃不淡，宛如一位入世未深的小伙子，尚未受到現實社會的洗禮，仍保留著那一點幼嫩卻會懂得為未來而擔憂，這顯得脫俗的中庸之道，真令人懷念。<br />\n<br />\n滑嫩的肉粒，粒粒分明，入口即溶，配上粟米汁，頓時洗脫了肉類原有的野性，變成一隻溫馴的野獸。<br />\n<br />\n美味可口的食物，總是讓人的胃口大開，止不住的一口又一口吃進肚。<br />\n<br />\n結果，枱上那杯檸檬茶絲毫未動，反而眼前只剩下一隻空碟。<br />\n<br />\n要是說豆腐火腩飯是男人的浪漫，那麼粟米肉粒飯代表著的就是善良之物。<br />\n<br />\n怎樣吃、何時吃、何地吃，亦是平淡得很。"},{"pid":"319fd422bc38dc5a8bc558dc0312bb5546b18dd0","tid":561432,"uid":42927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T05:06:55.000Z","msg":"飲著那杯檸檬茶，看了一會兒電視的畫面。<br />\n<br />\n飲到最後，任憑我怎用力的吸，亦再不能飲到一滴茶。<br />\n<br />\n意盡，就應離去，我走向收銀處，拿出厚厚的錢包。<br />\n<br />\n「埋單呀唔該。」我說。<br />\n<br />\n「四十三蚊。」姨姨說。<br />\n<br />\n我打開錢包，掏出了兩張二十蚊紙，再找找褲袋拿了三蚊出來。<br />\n<br />\n「四十⋯⋯三，齊數。」她收下了我錢。<br />\n<br />\n「拜拜。」我轉身踏出了門口，思緒卻仍留在茶記裡。<br />\n<br />\n由我進來坐下，落單，吃完，埋單。這步驟，我猜也是惟一多年來還未改變的事吧⋯⋯"},{"pid":"a5e7ca9565214f3a5cb4f52797391bf6df2b3ce1","tid":561432,"uid":125861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T05:09:10.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"ba7d32d40390712facfe40213c534e316f22b1d8","tid":561432,"uid":42927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a5e7ca9565214f3a5cb4f52797391bf6df2b3ce1","tid":561432,"uid":125861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T05:09:10.000Z","msg":"Lm"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T05:17:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多謝"},{"pid":"030bd2cd0a9229e9fd95a2cb35f1d8c688ca48e7","tid":561432,"uid":44149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T12:40:40.000Z","msg":"夠短<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"766f3e2f601ed0836d96b9cb5c9d863344bfa633","tid":561432,"uid":135265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T12:47:46.000Z","msg":"樓主，乜又係你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今次會唔會再爛尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/27.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"213fff9860a8d8c4925c204289822a4a897bbf13","tid":561432,"uid":42927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T22:21:50.000Z","msg":"「埋單呀唔該。」<br />\n<br />\n「廿七呀。」<br />\n<br />\n某一天，一餐粟米肉粒飯只盛惠二十七元正，已計加凍飲兩元。<br />\n<br />\n當然，那時的我還是位稚氣未脫的中學生，尚能享有廉價的學生餐。<br />\n<br />\n「點解你成日都食C餐嘅？」<br />\n<br />\n那時，Elaine偶爾會問我這個問題。<br />\n<br />\n「好食囉。」<br />\n<br />\n那時，我偶爾會答她這個問題。<br />\n<br />\n她是我中學時的女朋友，長髮馬尾，相當平庸的五官配上黑色粗框眼鏡。<br />\n<br />\n無論外貌、學業亦毫不出眾，毫不顯眼。<br />\n<br />\n這種女孩，能與我交疊上的因由，是因我倆也有修讀中國文學。<br />\n<br />\n剛拍拖時仍有一點點新鮮感，但保鮮期過後，任何食物也得腐爛，更何況與別人的關係。<br />\n<br />\n漸漸，我與她的話題離不開就是學業；可是，她與我的話題卻可牽連至昨日的早餐。<br />\n<br />\n這段關係本就不應存在，皆因中四方開學之際就似動物生態中的發春期，瞥見身邊的人各自都湊成了一對，我又怎能繼續單身下去呢？<br />\n<br />\n純粹只想一嘗戀愛的滋味，便決定打擾別人的人生。<br />\n<br />\n真是邪惡的人⋯⋯對吧？<br />\n<br />\n所以拍了三個月拖，我已在盤算如何與她分手。<br />\n<br />\n豈料到，竟被她捷足先登⋯⋯"},{"pid":"78f991ada913d2e2246301f7695b054f99cbae28","tid":561432,"uid":42927,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"030bd2cd0a9229e9fd95a2cb35f1d8c688ca48e7","tid":561432,"uid":44149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T12:40:40.000Z","msg":"夠短<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T22:23:20.000Z","msg":"話明短故<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過仲有啲，總之唔會超過一萬字啦。"},{"pid":"9f382098b8c816e1a0d5d57a5f1efc2667e0754d","tid":561432,"uid":42927,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"766f3e2f601ed0836d96b9cb5c9d863344bfa633","tid":561432,"uid":135265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T12:47:46.000Z","msg":"樓主，乜又係你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今次會唔會再爛尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/27.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T22:24:32.000Z","msg":"唔好派我膠住啦⋯⋯我從來都唔爛尾。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7d194ab0b3979ffcd6f07c2f8a85932671a5e34","tid":561432,"uid":42927,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T22:58:00.000Z","msg":"「Ben，對唔住呀，情人節嗰日我陪唔到你啦。」<br />\n<br />\n「嗯，哦⋯⋯」<br />\n<br />\n「喂呀！你唔問我點解嘅？你都唔緊張我嘅。」<br />\n<br />\n「哦⋯⋯點解呀？」<br />\n<br />\n「我嗰日要同屋企人食飯呀。」<br />\n<br />\n從那時開始，我方知道一個女人要說謊，真的很難看得穿。<br />\n<br />\n若然一個人要偷食，最普遍的情況也是利用他人作籍口，到你想指責她時，又會被會反罵你不信任她云云。<br />\n<br />\n結果，情人節之後的一個星期，她就向我提了分手，然後迅速與隔班的有錢仔阿Joe拍了拖。<br />\n<br />\n而情人節當天，我則在一間茶記，吃了一碟粟米肉粒飯。<br />\n<br />\n後來，聽朋友說Elaine在情人節那天一個人去了阿Joe的屋企，喝了點酒，便失身於他。<br />\n<br />\n老實說，我真的不介意被戴上綠帽，反正還能把我包裝成受害者，讓身邊的人為之憐憫，又不會沾上污名。<br />\n<br />\n再說白一點，眾生也不過是個偽善的皮囊，依賴著偽善之物讓自己好過一些。<br />\n<br />\n作為人類，我只是依從本性。"},{"pid":"73bff0415912f6383555af9f94b52bb0b43735e3","tid":561432,"uid":2536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T00:20:34.000Z","msg":"你氹到李海純笑未呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81baa5441475d67013ab21e03c20cab3b5f79e9a","tid":561432,"uid":42927,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"73bff0415912f6383555af9f94b52bb0b43735e3","tid":561432,"uid":2536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T00:20:34.000Z","msg":"你氹到李海純笑未呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T01:05:43.000Z","msg":"我諗緊點氹呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 畀啲時間我"},{"pid":"0b19d1b04d28b567972348aa26ff56cb992db28c","tid":561432,"uid":59269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T01:08:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83ad62cfd95b6ef653b6f90864c4c6564c4015e0","tid":561432,"uid":42927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b19d1b04d28b567972348aa26ff56cb992db28c","tid":561432,"uid":59269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T01:08:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T01:14:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 新年快樂，拎利是啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes1000.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe84f80eafc783aaa8f08aa0a805f13a79a2657b","tid":561432,"uid":42927,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T01:45:43.000Z","msg":"而為了將這種本性發揮得淋漓盡致，藉以證明我是個人類。<br />\n<br />\n大學一年級時，我去了信耶穌。<br />\n<br />\n諷刺的是我不信這世上有神的存在。<br />\n<br />\n只是恰巧被位大學同學哄小孩似哄了去教會，她叫Christine，與我同樣是文學院的學生，迥異的是她是一位基督徒。<br />\n<br />\n要論盡大學的眾生相，恐怕用上一天的時間亦不夠。<br />\n<br />\n但總有一些人，是特別惹起我的注意，Christine就是其中之一。<br />\n<br />\n打從第一眼開始，她高挑的身材以及醉人的容貌，還有純得像個奇葩的性枱，無不誘惑着我，於是我找上了她。<br />\n<br />\n由於我倆有著閱讀這共有興趣，很快便已混熟了。<br />\n<br />\n漸漸有着聊天的習慣，關係也一步一步的建立了起來。<br />\n<br />\n「喂喂～你想唔想跟我返教會呀？」某次，她有點忸怩的問我。<br />\n<br />\n「教會？」我吃驚的問。<br />\n<br />\n「係呀，一齊返教會啦，嚟啦～」她續說。<br />\n<br />\n「好呀，冇問題呀。」接著，我二話不說的答應了。<br />\n<br />\n因為我的目標非常清晰，雖然時機尚未成熟。<br />\n<br />\n我要得到她的肉體。"},{"pid":"1e55172750987f168f21a32ae789adc3e41afbc2","tid":561432,"uid":42927,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T02:08:47.000Z","msg":"想要得到一位基督徒的處女之身，確是難事。<br />\n<br />\n所以我必須進一步的接近她，不惜違背自身的思想，亦要拆開她的防線。<br />\n<br />\n而結果，我花了一年的時間。<br />\n<br />\n那一年，我每個星期都要跟著她參加那些無聊的教會活動，譬如說祈禱、唱聖詩、讀聖經、每日感謝主等等。<br />\n<br />\n儘管如此，仍未動搖我對於神的否定。<br />\n<br />\n假設有人告訴你，你的銀行戶口有一千萬但要你仙遊後才拿到，那麼你能相信他的說話嗎？<br />\n<br />\n偽善者就定然會相信，因要貫徹「偽」的信念。<br />\n<br />\n另一種選擇相信的人，就似Christine這種蠢女人。<br />\n<br />\n同一年，我每個星期都花盡心思盤算着如何哄騙她上床。<br />\n<br />\n先把一切的親密接觸合理化，還要一個浪漫的藉口。<br />\n<br />\n直到大學二年級時的情人節，我終於得逞⋯⋯"},{"pid":"f66fe3d98251337cf15b38842bb98b0ecec0612f","tid":561432,"uid":42927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T02:20:35.000Z","msg":"有冇人睇緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，為求寫實，跟住有啲甜，接受唔到可以飛咗佢。"},{"pid":"12addab3a41738b21879542bcd5d76ed8b361740","tid":561432,"uid":163253,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f66fe3d98251337cf15b38842bb98b0ecec0612f","tid":561432,"uid":42927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T02:20:35.000Z","msg":"有冇人睇緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，為求寫實，跟住有啲甜，接受唔到可以飛咗佢。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T02:46:59.000Z","msg":"有<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cfcfd17ebb299b08d246e99740e285b68ed85f0","tid":561432,"uid":35620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T02:49:33.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"75cad8daaf930f00c9f114bc85900b3864d280de","tid":561432,"uid":73670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T02:50:48.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"49ae94a54b3221487858148b256aa8de5b5e8d87","tid":561432,"uid":59269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T02:57:58.000Z","msg":"飲完茶就有文<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bf000466be86155970d0f3f45f1dfc1807ab564","tid":561432,"uid":42927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T03:14:28.000Z","msg":"事前，我買了點酒，還準備好了一盒condom放在房間，以防弄出人命。並且支開了父母，以確保晚上的家中空無一人。<br />\n<br />\n苦苦等到當日中午，我便前往這場早早安排好的約會。<br />\n<br />\n會合的地點是地鐵站的出口，今天的Christine上身穿著啡色的外套和灰色的T恤，而下身卻是一條牛仔長褲，一會兒可能有點難脫⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n我一瞧見Christine，便快步上前牽起她的手。<br />\n<br />\n只顧在玩手機的Christine頓時一呆，然後又甜絲絲的笑着說：「咦⋯⋯乜你咁快到嘅？」<br />\n<br />\n「掛住你嘛。」說罷肉麻之話後，我便湊近了身子吻吻她撩人的嘴脣，「呢隻唇膏啲味好甜。」<br />\n<br />\n「乜係咩？」她抿嘴一嘗，再訕訕的笑道：「你好白痴呀⋯⋯」<br />\n<br />\n「邊度白痴喎？」我問。<br />\n<br />\n「你嘅全部都咁白痴。」她說。<br />\n<br />\n「咁即係邊度白⋯⋯」<br />\n<br />\n未待我說罷，她忽爾傻呼呼的把頭埋進我的懷裡，然後嬌嗔地說：「喂呀～咪講住先啦，餓死我啦，你快啲帶我食嘢先啦～」<br />\n<br />\n「好啦好啦，行啦。」<br />\n<br />\n如是者，我倆便去到附近一間商場的餐廳吃了頓午餐，接著又買了兩張電影戲飛。<br />\n<br />\n對於這些例行公事，也不過是消磨一下時間，好讓我快點到達晚上。"},{"pid":"b0d73444932ae43bce015164532f9f53babb1361","tid":561432,"uid":65424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T03:18:13.000Z","msg":"個開頭令我諗起大文豪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ac3bb8bb45d3fa53561aaf7c6fe47f4b6438736","tid":561432,"uid":42927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b0d73444932ae43bce015164532f9f53babb1361","tid":561432,"uid":65424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T03:18:13.000Z","msg":"個開頭令我諗起大文豪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T03:48:15.000Z","msg":"邊度似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc7b3a7e18bcac5960fef4b4be07748da7c2d4a5","tid":561432,"uid":126779,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b0d73444932ae43bce015164532f9f53babb1361","tid":561432,"uid":65424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T03:18:13.000Z","msg":"個開頭令我諗起大文豪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T03:57:10.000Z","msg":"今天不小心點了個粟米肉粒飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2276b296c00d71730ace8da2f9608629c81a21c","tid":561432,"uid":135265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f382098b8c816e1a0d5d57a5f1efc2667e0754d","tid":561432,"uid":42927,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"766f3e2f601ed0836d96b9cb5c9d863344bfa633","tid":561432,"uid":135265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T12:47:46.000Z","msg":"樓主，乜又係你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今次會唔會再爛尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/27.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T22:24:32.000Z","msg":"唔好派我膠住啦⋯⋯我從來都唔爛尾。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T04:40:02.000Z","msg":"呀純都依家都未識笑，嗰本紅樓夢睇咗幾耐先睇完<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：試過忍唔住騎劫你兩次<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c9390c657b616273ec37e64142feea63a037311","tid":561432,"uid":135265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T04:42:36.000Z","msg":"行文風格唔同咗，啲文筆都進步咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00be5ab02f5b2ae283d6768d1df9b2a795f7d753","tid":561432,"uid":155246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T04:46:21.000Z","msg":"Lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a01705812f54ae89fa08078543dd8244cf84a1b","tid":561432,"uid":42927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c9390c657b616273ec37e64142feea63a037311","tid":561432,"uid":135265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T04:42:36.000Z","msg":"行文風格唔同咗，啲文筆都進步咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T05:24:15.000Z","msg":"這次是寫實類嘛，文筆我覺得自己還是一貫的差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw多謝你仲記得我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2db74449f6dedff27a2d67dca891e323b6c7f9f3","tid":561432,"uid":35192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T06:04:00.000Z","msg":"好文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce21d300f0e7365eca7d32e6c05a92c673445dfb","tid":561432,"uid":139373,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"d2276b296c00d71730ace8da2f9608629c81a21c","tid":561432,"uid":135265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f382098b8c816e1a0d5d57a5f1efc2667e0754d","tid":561432,"uid":42927,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"766f3e2f601ed0836d96b9cb5c9d863344bfa633","tid":561432,"uid":135265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T12:47:46.000Z","msg":"樓主，乜又係你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今次會唔會再爛尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/27.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T22:24:32.000Z","msg":"唔好派我膠住啦⋯⋯我從來都唔爛尾。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T04:40:02.000Z","msg":"呀純都依家都未識笑，嗰本紅樓夢睇咗幾耐先睇完<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：試過忍唔住騎劫你兩次<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T06:13:37.000Z","msg":"林黛王巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你係唔係講緊文科班？個故完咗啦喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"485474b1abd2ac0d936262c714ca567f50fa7adb","tid":561432,"uid":42927,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T07:40:12.000Z","msg":"看罷一齣很是無聊的賀歲片，竟讓Christine在途中失笑了下十次。<br />\n<br />\n離開戲院，我倆又逛了一會街道，街上的路人有老有嫩，亦似我倆也是一對一對的。<br />\n<br />\n不知不覺間，暮色漸濃，街道的色調亦逐漸的暗淡起來，由灰化成暗，直至頭上滲黃的街燈登場，宣告了夜幕已臨。<br />\n<br />\n我倆去到一間餐廳，吃了一頓情人節套餐。<br />\n<br />\n明明只是食物而已，卻可以包裝一番再添層次，但要是伸手拆開那張包裝紙一窺，便可知其不過是用以果腹之物，平平無奇。<br />\n<br />\n那到底價值何在？<br />\n<br />\n價值是任人定義的。<br />\n<br />\n對我而言，就是為了這天的目標埋點伏筆。<br />\n<br />\n在我吃罷這餐尚未離開餐廳之際，便趁著空出的時間，以去廁所作藉口，匆匆跑到對面街的花店，然後買了一束紫色的毋忘我。<br />\n<br />\n回到餐廳，只見Christine正帶點悶氣的等待著我。<br />\n<br />\n「乜咁鬼耐㗎你。」她說，言語間似有稍稍不滿。<br />\n<br />\n我把那一束花收在背後，逐步走近她，然後故作神秘的坐下來。<br />\n<br />\n「又話去廁所，去咁耐⋯⋯」她的話只說到一半。<br />\n<br />\n「為咗買花畀你呀嘛。」我便緩緩地把一束毋忘我雙手奉送給她。<br />\n<br />\n「吓⋯⋯」Christine登時極為愕然，呆呆的把花束接過去，但不消半刻，這種錯愕盡化成甜蜜之情，令她溢出世上最幸福的笑容。<br />\n<br />\n「嘻嘻～你做咩嘥埋呢啲錢呀⋯⋯」<br />\n<br />\n事實證明，沒有女孩不喜歡花。"},{"pid":"db796aeffaeeab473882c537d476b76b99b1f68c","tid":561432,"uid":44149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T08:08:23.000Z","msg":"上面唔提都唔記得<br />\n樓主幾時先寫埋個故<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42187ded0236047931711040c815e38b113f2231","tid":561432,"uid":135265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce21d300f0e7365eca7d32e6c05a92c673445dfb","tid":561432,"uid":139373,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"d2276b296c00d71730ace8da2f9608629c81a21c","tid":561432,"uid":135265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f382098b8c816e1a0d5d57a5f1efc2667e0754d","tid":561432,"uid":42927,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T22:24:32.000Z","msg":"唔好派我膠住啦⋯⋯我從來都唔爛尾。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T04:40:02.000Z","msg":"呀純都依家都未識笑，嗰本紅樓夢睇咗幾耐先睇完<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：試過忍唔住騎劫你兩次<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T06:13:37.000Z","msg":"林黛王巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你係唔係講緊文科班？個故完咗啦喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T09:01:09.000Z","msg":"林黛王喺上面呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我係騎得好差嗰位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d99ceeb25949ee6d352aefce8463657b5f64bdda","tid":561432,"uid":83440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T14:30:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85c86f7b074104b250016b0190c195e5f6c56623","tid":561432,"uid":143221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T14:40:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"14409b2ee2f3c0ad50ac557d0d8f011761eea49a","tid":561432,"uid":3688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T11:34:22.000Z","msg":"巴打又係你啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f427c9f8a46458f0c6c608c542f5204e34d233f2","tid":561432,"uid":46566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T12:01:51.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"52711f042c9142e6e9c1f089b93bb7c1e6866a92","tid":561432,"uid":3688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T13:14:15.000Z","msg":"樓主？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68db2ec6dab018777fa1661b51442cc31dde62d1","tid":561432,"uid":42927,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T10:01:52.000Z","msg":"女孩子皆喜歡花，卻不諳花能致命。<br />\n<br />\n現今世道，也不知多少女孩的心死於花堆之下，亡於男孩的花言巧語之中。<br />\n<br />\n所以說，越是浪漫的事物，就化成越尖的利刃，能一刀一刀割開女孩的衣裳。<br />\n<br />\n轉眼間，Christine已被我帶回到家中。<br />\n<br />\n從步入門口那一刻開始，她這獵物便已墮進我這獵人的圈套。<br />\n<br />\n儘管她上來我家之前很理性的告訴我不能有非分之想，但亦無阻我的計劃。<br />\n<br />\nChristine坐在客廳的沙發上，脫掉了外套放於一旁，望著眼前發光的電視機。<br />\n<br />\n另一邊廂的我，則在廚房拿了兩個酒杯和一枝紅酒出來。<br />\n<br />\n「咦⋯⋯你拎住枝咩嚟㗎？」她眨著眼睛問。<br />\n<br />\n我坐在她身旁，一邊替她倒酒，一邊說道：「呢支咪紅酒囉。」<br />\n<br />\n「吓？」她聽後一怔，幽幽的說：「我唔飲酒㗎，飲酒唔健康㗎。」<br />\n<br />\n「呢啲酒唔同㗎，飲紅酒可以抗氧化，令你啲皮膚再靚啲，好健康㗎。」我正說服著她，「同埋你之前唔係話想學猜枚嘅？咁猜枚要飲酒㗎嘛，我依家教你啦，輸咗先要飲。」<br />\n<br />\n「但係⋯⋯」Christine似是仍有所顧慮，「但係啲酒難唔難飲㗎？」<br />\n<br />\n「你飲啖咪知囉。」我把裝着紅酒的酒杯遞給她。<br />\n<br />\n「哦⋯⋯」她淺嘗一口，面有難色的再道：「嘩～好酸呀。」<br />\n<br />\n「健康嘢係咁㗎啦，係難入口少少。」我說。<br />\n<br />\n「咁呀⋯⋯咁好囉，你教我玩猜枚啦。」Christine的態度終於有點軟化。<br />\n<br />\n之後，我便教她玩猜枚，每輸一次都要喝一口紅酒，不出十局，她便喝罷了一杯，然後我又為她倒了一杯。<br />\n<br />\n「十。」<br />\n<br />\n「十五。」<br />\n<br />\n「收哂。」<br />\n<br />\n「喂呀～我又輸咗啦。」Christine很是不忿的道：「唔制呀～你次次都唔讓我！」<br />\n<br />\n「咁你係新手呀嘛。」我說。<br />\n<br />\n「衰人～」她拿起酒杯，又喝一口，只見她兩邊臉頰已漸漸透紅，說話也有點亂。<br />\n<br />\nChristine的性格本來就不喜失敗，如今在猜枚上敗於我，亦自然不願服輸，勢要打敗我，故才可騙她喝下三、四杯酒。<br />\n<br />\n紅酒易醉，女孩的防線亦易碎。<br />\n<br />\n不一會兒，Christine又輸掉數局，她的臉龐已經通紅，身體更似是很熱的冒出了汗，讓她整個人看起來水汪汪的，非常動人。<br />\n<br />\n看來，我即將得手了⋯⋯"},{"pid":"5a9d073176af3efe93a88a1b7f940c4cee7647ed","tid":561432,"uid":42927,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T10:58:48.000Z","msg":"女孩的心，同時能失於酒香之下。<br />\n<br />\n一杯醇醪，背後固然是不懷好意。<br />\n<br />\n因醉翁之意從來不在酒⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\nChristine再輸一局爾後，便稍現慍色的道：「我唔玩住啦～我要去廁所呀～」<br />\n<br />\n「哦，好呀。」<br />\n<br />\n只見她緩緩的站起來，醉醺醺的姿態昭然若揭，步履蹣跚的她也不知正走向何處。<br />\n<br />\n「Ben呀～你屋企廁所喺邊㗎？」她靠著牆壁問我。<br />\n<br />\n「直行轉右對門呀。」<br />\n<br />\n「唔知呀⋯⋯你帶我去啦⋯⋯頭好暈呀⋯⋯」<br />\n<br />\n「好呀⋯⋯」<br />\n<br />\n見狀的我，便上前抱著她柔軟的身子，一步一步把她帶到我偌大的房間，然後輕放她在我的床上。<br />\n<br />\nChristine似是疲倦得很的躺在床上，又是迷迷糊糊似的。<br />\n<br />\n如此的她，儼如放在砧板上的豬肉，已任我魚肉。<br />\n<br />\n「喂呀～呢度⋯⋯邊度呀～我要去廁所呀～」她的口中唸唸有詞。<br />\n<br />\n我坐在床邊，凝望着Christine的容顏與嬌軀，不由得心裡一蕩，皆因眼前的一切已屬於我的。<br />\n<br />\n我並沒有開燈，在這昏暗的環境下，只靠窗邊滲進微光去完成接著的一切事情。<br />\n<br />\n在我下手的一刻，便決定了捨棄人性，只保留交配的本能，我先湊近身子抱著她軟綿綿的身軀，Christine的皮膚很白很滑，髮線又長又順，摸上來真的很舒服似的。<br />\n<br />\n聞著她身上獨有的處女香與酒味混和一體，讓我又興奮了一重。<br />\n<br />\n正當我的雙唇遊走於她的頸與鎖骨之間，雙手亦從腰身摸到她的胸脯去。<br />\n<br />\n即使隔着衣服和胸圍，亦感受到Christine的胸部手感不錯，她的乳房大小恰好，軟得像棉花一樣。<br />\n<br />\n接著，我便退後一點再向著下身埋手，伸出雙手解開她的褲頭⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n「Ben⋯⋯」<br />\n<br />\n驀地，我聽到Christine喚叫著我的名字，她的聲線竟令我開啟了聖人模式⋯⋯"},{"pid":"441b92c40ea16e016f00299e46acabbc54e5c107","tid":561432,"uid":42927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14409b2ee2f3c0ad50ac557d0d8f011761eea49a","tid":561432,"uid":3688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T11:34:22.000Z","msg":"巴打又係你啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T11:03:00.000Z","msg":"冇錯，又係我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49c99510e7d006f41bc3e7b9ac8de166119a14a9","tid":561432,"uid":124330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T11:50:47.000Z","msg":"留名加速<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aea654f828eef57e3ade60ef09693bae3f38522","tid":561432,"uid":97776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T12:00:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <im